general.title: Centenary
general.description: Win 100 games in Quick or Competitive Play.

general.title: Undying
general.description: Get a 20 player kill streak in Quick or Competitive Play.

general.title: Survival Expert
general.description: Use health packs to heal 900 health in a single life in Quick or Competitive Play.

general.title: Decorated
general.description: Earn 50 postgame medals in Quick or Competitive Play.

general.title: Blackjack
general.description: Earn 21 postgame cards in Quick or Competitive Play.

general.title: The Friend Zone
general.description: Play a Quick or Competitive Play game in a group with a friend.

damage.title: Slice and Dice
damage.description: Kill 4 enemies with a single use of Genji's Dragonblade in Quick or Competitive Play.

damage.title: Their Own Worst Enemy
damage.description: Kill 2 enemies with a single use of Genji's Deflection in Quick or Competitive Play.

damage.title: Whoa There!
damage.description: Interrupt an enemy ultimate ability with Cassidy's Flashbang in Quick or Competitive Play.

damage.title: Clearing the Area
damage.description: Knock an enemy to their death using Pharah's Concussive Blast in Quick or Competitive Play.

damage.title: Rocket Man
damage.description: Get 2 killing blows with a single use of Soldier: 76's Helix Rockets in Quick or Competitive Play.

damage.title: Target Rich Environment
damage.description: Kill 4 enemies with a single use of Soldier: 76's Tactical Visor in Quick or Competitive Play.

damage.title: Total Recall
damage.description: Recover 400 health using Tracer's Recall without dying in Quick or Competitive Play.

damage.title: Special Delivery
damage.description: Stick 4 of Tracer's Pulse Bombs onto enemies in a single Quick or Competitive Play game.

damage.title: Triple Threat
damage.description: Kill 2 enemies in each of Bastion's configurations without dying in Quick or Competitive Play.

damage.title: The Dragon Is Sated
damage.description: Kill 4 enemies with one of Hanzo's Spirit Dragons in Quick or Competitive Play.

damage.title: Ice Blocked
damage.description: Block 1200 damage with a single use of Mei's Ice Wall in Quick or Competitive Play.

damage.title: Smooth as Silk
damage.description: Kill an enemy with a scoped headshot while airborne as Widowmaker in Quick or Competitive Play.

damage.title: The Car Wash
damage.description: Hit an enemy with 3 beams simultaneously as Symmetra in Quick or Competitive Play.

damage.title: Huge Success
damage.description: Teleport 20 allies in a single Quick or Competitive Play game as Symmetra.

damage.title: Hack the Planet
damage.description: Hack 15 enemies without dying as Sombra in Quick or Competitive Play.

damage.title: Power Outage
damage.description: Hack 6 enemies at once as Sombra in Quick or Competitive Play.

damage.title: Short Fuse
damage.description: Kill an enemy by shooting Ashe’s Dynamite from at least 30 meters away in Quick or Competitive Play.

tank.title: Shot Down
tank.description: Prevent 1500 damage with a single use of D.va's Defense Matrix in Quick or Competitive Play.

tank.title: Game Over
tank.description: Kill 4 enemies with a single use of D.va's Self Destruct in Quick or Competitive Play.

tank.title: Storm, Earth and Fire
tank.description: Land Reinhardt's Fire Strike and Charge after an Earthshatter stun in Quick or Competitive Play.

tank.title: Giving You the Hook
tank.description: Interrupt an enemy ultimate ability with Roadhog's Hook in Quick or Competitive Play.

tank.title: Hog Wild
tank.description: Knock 2 enemies to their deaths with one use of Roadhog's Whole Hog in Quick or Competitive Play.

tank.title: Anger Management
tank.description: Damage 6 enemies during a single use of Winston's Primal Rage in Quick or Competitive Play.

tank.title: Power Overwhelming
tank.description: Keep Zarya's particle cannon above 70 power for 60 seconds in Quick or Competitive Play.

tank.title: The Power of Attraction
tank.description: Capture 5 enemies in a single use of Zarya's Graviton Surge in Quick or Competitive Play.

tank.title: Adaptation
tank.description: Absorb 1500 damage with Wrecking Ball's Adaptive Shield without dying in Quick or Competitive Play.

tank.title: Strike
tank.description: Roll through 4 enemies within 2 seconds as Wrecking Ball in Quick or Competitive Play.

tank.title: Event Horizon
tank.description: Get 3 killing blows during a single use of Sigma's Gravitic Flux in Quick or Competitive Play.

tank.title: Conservation of Energy
tank.description: Gain 350 shields with a single use of Sigma's Kinetic Grasp in Quick or Competitive Play.

support.title: Supersonic
support.description: Block 1000 damage with a single use of Lúcio's Sound Barrier in Quick or Competitive Play.

support.title: Group Health Plan
support.description: Restore 200 health for 5 allies without dying as Mercy in Quick or Competitive Play.

support.title: Naptime
support.description: Interrupt an enemy ultimate ability with Ana's Sleep Dart in Quick or Competitive Play.

support.title: Enabler
support.description: Get 4 kills or assists with a single use of Ana's Nano Boost in Quick or Competitive Play.

support.title: Antipode
support.description: Hit 7 targets simultaneously with Moira's Coalescence in Quick or Competitive Play.

support.title: Simple Trigonometry
support.description: Fully deplete both types of Moira's Biotic Orb without dying in Quick or Competitive Play.

support.title: Grounded
support.description: Kill an airborne enemy with Brigitte's Whip Shot in Quick or Competitive Play.

support.title: Excuse Me
support.description: Interrupt an enemy ultimate ability with Brigitte's Shield Bash in Quick or Competitive Play.

maps.title: Lockdown
maps.description: Win a Capture map on defense without losing the first objective in Quick or Competitive Play.

maps.title: Double Cap
maps.description: Capture both objectives on a Capture map without dying in Quick or Competitive Play.

maps.title: Escort Duty
maps.description: Push a payload 100 meters without leaving it in Quick or Competitive Play.

maps.title: Can't Touch This
maps.description: Prevent the attacking team from touching the payload for 1 minute in Quick or Competitive Play.

maps.title: Shutout
maps.description: Win a Control map without the enemy capturing an objective in Quick or Competitive Play.

maps.title: World Traveler
maps.description: Win a Quick or Competitive Play game on 12 different maps.

maps.title: Flagbearer
maps.description: Win Capture the Flag with a score of 3 to 0.

maps.title: Captured
maps.description: Capture a flag in a game of Capture the Flag.

maps.title: Delivery Interruption
maps.description: Kill an enemy as they carry the flag in a game of Capture the Flag.

events.title: Volley
events.description: Score a goal in Lúcioball with a shot taken from at least 4 meters in the air.

events.title: Safe Hands
events.description: Score 3 saves in a row in Lúcioball.

events.title: Lúcio Hat Trick
events.description: Score a goal, a save, and an assist in a game of Lúcioball.

events.title: Maelstrom
events.description: Complete Storm Rising (Story) on Expert difficulty.

events.title: Tempest
events.description: Complete Storm Rising (Story) on Hard difficulty.

events.title: Molten Cores
events.description: Complete the Molten Cores Archives challenge mission.
